    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Banzai Escape 2 Subterranean is a sequel game based on the events of Banzai Escape 2 where the Draugr labs have been captured by SPECTRE. All of the sisters (Inchester, Imingter and Iekler) take in refugees to a location deep underground. In order to survive, they must defeat the Lanun occupying the underground dungeon networks along with other factions such as SPECTRE and others</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an Elite Imingter agent with special access to roaming around underground networks to dispose any incoming threat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Lets Journey Underground Subterranean network<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/d044ffdfda5f802ed45973c78cbb1472.poster.avif?t=1764133453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/d044ffdfda5f802ed45973c78cbb1472.webm?t=1764133453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/d044ffdfda5f802ed45973c78cbb1472.mp4?t=1764133453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engaging Enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/c7f67791bf6f5a82780da91be638fcaf.poster.avif?t=1764133453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/c7f67791bf6f5a82780da91be638fcaf.webm?t=1764133453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/c7f67791bf6f5a82780da91be638fcaf.mp4?t=1764133453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Completing Missions</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/abc796107af2824fd1f241af7e6d6f3d.poster.avif?t=1764133453\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/abc796107af2824fd1f241af7e6d6f3d.webm?t=1764133453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/abc796107af2824fd1f241af7e6d6f3d.mp4?t=1764133453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1P or 2P</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/a926a683349cd877b4a84df3cbd5aa8b.avif?t=1764133453\" width=616 height=217 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player / Co-op mode to allow friend to play together.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fun! Chaotic! Intense!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/91ba316f7f61dfc0cc02702b9d2ab1f9.avif?t=1764133453\" width=616 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player will always be encountering action moment with rogue and aggressive like of enemies while finishing your objectives</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizable</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/1cf5b380105d3822859aaf40f7f974d9.avif?t=1764133453\" width=616 height=490 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable costumes / skins. Lots varieties of options to choose to make your character looks prettier.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Random Generated Level</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/6d12fdff4275f78508c45b0b8e21cc83.avif?t=1764133453\" width=616 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random generate map segments to allow different path taken toward objectives area inside underground dungeon</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RNG Arsenals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/08d447d644e601487898f71bde2c3a04.avif?t=1764133453\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random generate gun &amp; powerups or loot-able for grinding. Lots of guns and about 56++ nano-plugin addon powerups skills with lots of random stats that can be obtainable. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >..And Many more!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758950/extras/65933dec28846ab26790adce8331fc2a.avif?t=1764133453\" width=616 height=179 /></span> </p>",
